{"tid":1879452,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"唔想佢唔開心","createTime":"2020-02-14T08:09:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-15T19:47:31.000Z","uid":142861,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"62c414ca720e4d6ed913d73cce5bec5589107b6e","tid":1879452,"uid":142861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T08:09:58.000Z","msg":"有時佢會莫名奇妙地唔開心 <br />\n我唔想見到佢咁<br />\n見到佢唔開心我就會同佢一樣唔開心<br />\n佢要我坦白 唔可以瞞住佢自己一個唔開心 <br />\n之後佢就會黎氹我<br />\n但佢自己有時就會將啲負面情緒收收埋埋自己承受 唔想俾我知<br />\n真係唔想佢咁 我真係好想佢開心同幫到佢<br />\n覺得自己好無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我真係好愛你架 女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6c79ea0bc6e41d1a9f5686790e682633e3ae49c","tid":1879452,"uid":276711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T08:29:06.000Z","msg":"樓主真係好愛你女朋友<br />\n諗住點陪佢過情人節"},{"pid":"1e0ad838ecdb6e75dec5d4cdaf5a9dd6a5a8d557","tid":1879452,"uid":142861,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f6c79ea0bc6e41d1a9f5686790e682633e3ae49c","tid":1879452,"uid":276711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T08:29:06.000Z","msg":"樓主真係好愛你女朋友<br />\n諗住點陪佢過情人節"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T08:48:13.000Z","msg":"佢唔想我周圍去 所以想留係屋企陪佢就夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"491f9de3ff39dca795c47071658a6d21d7e430c6","tid":1879452,"uid":276711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e0ad838ecdb6e75dec5d4cdaf5a9dd6a5a8d557","tid":1879452,"uid":142861,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f6c79ea0bc6e41d1a9f5686790e682633e3ae49c","tid":1879452,"uid":276711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T08:29:06.000Z","msg":"樓主真係好愛你女朋友<br />\n諗住點陪佢過情人節"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T08:48:13